1
00:00:07,542 --> 00:00:09,875
Katara: WATER...

2
00:00:09,917 --> 00:00:11,458
EARTH...

3
00:00:11,500 --> 00:00:13,709
FIRE...

4
00:00:13,750 --> 00:00:16,417
AIR.

5
00:00:16,458 --> 00:00:20,375
LONG AGO, THE FOUR NATIONS LIVED
TOGETHER IN HARMONY.

6
00:00:20,417 --> 00:00:24,750
THEN EVERYTHING CHANGED
WHEN THE FIRE NATION ATTACKED.

7
00:00:24,792 --> 00:00:28,667
ONLY THE AVATAR,
MASTER OF ALL FOUR ELEMENTS,
COULD STOP THEM.

8
00:00:28,709 --> 00:00:32,625
BUT WHEN THE WORLD
NEEDED HIM MOST, HE VANISHED.

9
00:00:32,667 --> 00:00:36,166
100 YEARS PASSED
AND MY BROTHER AND I DISCOVERED
THE NEW AVATAR...

10
00:00:36,208 --> 00:00:38,250
AN AIRBENDER NAMED AANG.

11
00:00:38,291 --> 00:00:40,709
AND ALTHOUGH HIS AIRBENDING
SKILLS ARE GREAT

12
00:00:40,750 --> 00:00:43,709
HE HAS A LOT TO LEARN BEFORE
HE'S READY TO SAVE ANYONE.

13
00:00:43,750 --> 00:00:47,834
BUT I BELIEVE AANG
CAN SAVE THE WORLD.

14
00:00:47,875 --> 00:00:49,625
♪

15
00:00:55,792 --> 00:00:57,959
Aang: SO WHAT'S THE NEW PLAN?

16
00:00:58,000 --> 00:01:00,083
Sokka: THE NEW PLAN
IS THE OLD PLAN.

17
00:01:00,125 --> 00:01:02,375
YOU JUST NEED TO MASTER
ALL FOUR ELEMENTS

18
00:01:02,417 --> 00:01:04,750
AND CONFRONT THE FIRE LORD
BEFORE THE COMET COMES.

19
00:01:04,792 --> 00:01:06,834
WHERE AM I SUPPOSED TO GET
A FIREBENDING TEACHER?

20
00:01:06,875 --> 00:01:07,834
HELLO.

21
00:01:07,875 --> 00:01:09,709
ZUKO HERE.

22
00:01:09,750 --> 00:01:14,083
I THINK IT'S TIME
I JOINED YOUR GROUP AND TAUGHT
THE AVATAR FIREBENDING

23
00:01:14,125 --> 00:01:18,333
AND I KNOW MY DESTINY
IS TO HELP YOU RESTORE
BALANCE TO THE WORLD.

24
00:01:18,375 --> 00:01:21,041
I THINK YOU<i> ARE</i> SUPPOSED TO BE
MY FIREBENDING TEACHER.

25
00:01:23,041 --> 00:01:27,041
[MEN VOCALIZING RHYTHMICALLY]

26
00:01:30,041 --> 00:01:33,250
Zuko: I KNOW YOU'RE NERVOUS,
BUT REMEMBER, FIREBENDING

27
00:01:33,291 --> 00:01:36,333
IN AND OF ITSELF
IS NOT SOMETHING TO FEAR.

28
00:01:36,375 --> 00:01:37,959
[SIGHING]

29
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:39,208
OK.

30
00:01:39,250 --> 00:01:40,500
NOT SOMETHING TO FEAR.

31
00:01:40,542 --> 00:01:42,375
BUT IF YOU DON'T RESPECT IT

32
00:01:42,417 --> 00:01:44,959
IT'LL CHEW YOU UP
AND SPIT YOU OUT
LIKE AN ANGRY KOMODO RHINO.

33
00:01:45,041 --> 00:01:46,375
[GASPING]

34
00:01:46,417 --> 00:01:47,917
NOW, SHOW ME WHAT YOU'VE GOT.

35
00:01:47,959 --> 00:01:49,959
ANY AMOUNT OF FIRE YOU CAN MAKE.

36
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:52,208
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

37
00:01:57,041 --> 00:01:59,458
MAYBE I NEED
A LITTLE MORE INSTRUCTION.

38
00:01:59,500 --> 00:02:01,709
PERHAPS A DEMONSTRATION?

39
00:02:01,750 --> 00:02:03,000
Zuko: GOOD IDEA.

40
00:02:03,041 --> 00:02:05,208
YOU MIGHT WANT TO TAKE
A COUPLE STEPS BACK.

41
00:02:05,875 --> 00:02:07,125
[INHALES]

42
00:02:07,667 --> 00:02:11,500
[GRUNTING]

43
00:02:11,542 --> 00:02:13,000
WHAT WAS THAT?

44
00:02:13,041 --> 00:02:15,417
THAT WAS THE WORST FIREBENDING
I'VE EVER SEEN.

45
00:02:15,458 --> 00:02:18,375
I THOUGHT IT WAS NICE.

46
00:02:18,417 --> 00:02:21,542
[GRUNTING]

47
00:02:21,583 --> 00:02:23,709
[GROANING]

48
00:02:23,750 --> 00:02:25,333
WHY IS THIS HAPPENING?

49
00:02:25,375 --> 00:02:27,750
MAYBE IT'S THE ALTITUDE.

50
00:02:27,792 --> 00:02:29,208
YEAH, COULD BE.

51
00:02:34,625 --> 00:02:38,250
[GRUNTING...]

52
00:02:38,291 --> 00:02:39,375
[YAWNING]

53
00:02:39,417 --> 00:02:42,750
JUST BREATHE, AND...

54
00:02:42,792 --> 00:02:44,875
THAT ONE KIND OF FELT HOT.

55
00:02:44,917 --> 00:02:46,041
DON'T PATRONIZE ME.

56
00:02:46,083 --> 00:02:47,959
YOU KNOW WHAT IT'S
SUPPOSED TO LOOK LIKE.

57
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:49,667
SORRY, SIFU HOTMAN.

58
00:02:49,709 --> 00:02:52,959
AND STOP CALLING ME THAT.

59
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:56,333
Sokka: HEY, JERKS.

60
00:02:56,375 --> 00:02:59,542
MIND IF I WATCH YOU TWO JERKS
DO YOUR JERK BENDING?

61
00:02:59,583 --> 00:03:01,333
GET OUT OF HERE.

62
00:03:01,375 --> 00:03:02,834
OK, TAKE IT EASY.

63
00:03:02,875 --> 00:03:03,875
I WAS JUST KIDDING AROUND.

64
00:03:03,917 --> 00:03:05,500
[CHUCKLING]

65
00:03:05,542 --> 00:03:06,709
JERK BENDING.

66
00:03:06,750 --> 00:03:08,417
STILL GOT IT.

67
00:03:08,458 --> 00:03:12,375
[GROANING]

68
00:03:12,417 --> 00:03:14,667
[GROWLING]

69
00:03:20,500 --> 00:03:22,041
Zuko: LISTEN, EVERYBODY.

70
00:03:22,083 --> 00:03:23,917
I'VE GOT SOME PRETTY BAD NEWS.

71
00:03:23,959 --> 00:03:25,625
I'VE LOST MY STUFF.

72
00:03:25,667 --> 00:03:26,917
DON'T LOOK AT ME.

73
00:03:26,959 --> 00:03:29,000
I DIDN'T TOUCH YOUR STUFF.

74
00:03:29,041 --> 00:03:31,166
I'M TALKING ABOUT
MY FIREBENDING.

75
00:03:31,208 --> 00:03:32,709
IT'S GONE.

76
00:03:32,750 --> 00:03:36,333
[KATARA LAUGHING]

77
00:03:36,375 --> 00:03:37,625
I'M SORRY.

78
00:03:37,667 --> 00:03:39,208
I'M JUST LAUGHING AT THE IRONY.

79
00:03:39,250 --> 00:03:41,000
YOU KNOW, HOW IT WOULD'VE
BEEN NICE FOR US

80
00:03:41,041 --> 00:03:43,250
IF YOU'D LOST YOUR FIREBENDING
A LONG TIME AGO?

81
00:03:43,291 --> 00:03:44,625
WELL, IT'S NOT LOST.

82
00:03:44,667 --> 00:03:47,834
IT'S JUST WEAKER
FOR SOME REASON.

83
00:03:47,875 --> 00:03:50,125
MAYBE YOU'RE JUST NOT AS GOOD
AS YOU THINK YOU ARE.

84
00:03:50,166 --> 00:03:52,375
OUCH.

85
00:03:52,417 --> 00:03:54,291
[GROWLING]

86
00:03:54,333 --> 00:03:56,625
I BET IT'S BECAUSE
I CHANGED SIDES.

87
00:03:56,667 --> 00:03:58,417
THAT'S RIDICULOUS.

88
00:03:58,458 --> 00:03:59,417
I DON'T KNOW.

89
00:03:59,458 --> 00:04:01,208
MAYBE IT ISN'T.

90
00:04:01,250 --> 00:04:03,709
MAYBE YOUR FIREBENDING
COMES FROM RAGE

91
00:04:03,750 --> 00:04:06,875
AND YOU JUST DON'T HAVE
ENOUGH ANGER TO FUEL IT
THE WAY YOU USED TO.

92
00:04:06,917 --> 00:04:10,375
SO ALL WE NEED TO DO
IS MAKE ZUKO ANGRY.

93
00:04:10,625 --> 00:04:11,959
EASY ENOUGH.

94
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:15,041
[LAUGHING]

95
00:04:15,083 --> 00:04:16,291
OK, CUT IT OUT!

96
00:04:16,333 --> 00:04:18,875
LOOK.

97
00:04:18,917 --> 00:04:21,291
EVEN IF YOU'RE RIGHT,
I DON'T WANT TO RELY
ON HATE AND ANGER ANYMORE.

98
00:04:21,333 --> 00:04:23,709
THERE HAS TO BE ANOTHER WAY.

99
00:04:23,750 --> 00:04:27,250
YOU'RE GONNA NEED TO LEARN
TO DRAW YOUR FIREBENDING
FROM A DIFFERENT SOURCE.

100
00:04:27,291 --> 00:04:29,625
I RECOMMEND THE ORIGINAL SOURCE.

101
00:04:29,667 --> 00:04:31,250
HOW'S HE SUPPOSED TO DO THAT?

102
00:04:31,291 --> 00:04:33,000
BY JUMPING INTO A VOLCANO?

103
00:04:33,041 --> 00:04:35,583
NO.

104
00:04:35,625 --> 00:04:38,667
ZUKO NEEDS TO GO BACK
TO WHATEVER THE ORIGINAL
SOURCE OF FIREBENDING IS.

105
00:04:38,709 --> 00:04:40,875
SO IS IT JUMPING INTO A VOLCANO?

106
00:04:40,917 --> 00:04:42,750
I DON'T KNOW.

107
00:04:42,792 --> 00:04:45,792
FOR EARTHBENDING, THE ORIGINAL
BENDERS WERE BADGERMOLES.

108
00:04:45,834 --> 00:04:49,333
ONE DAY, WHEN I WAS LITTLE,
I RAN AWAY AND HID IN A CAVE.

109
00:04:49,375 --> 00:04:50,250
[CRYING]

110
00:04:50,291 --> 00:04:54,000
[CRASHING]

111
00:04:54,041 --> 00:04:55,542
THAT'S WHERE I MET THEM.

112
00:04:55,583 --> 00:04:58,834
[GROWLING]

113
00:04:58,875 --> 00:05:04,125
[LAUGHING]

114
00:05:04,709 --> 00:05:09,834
THEY WERE BLIND, JUST LIKE ME,
SO WE UNDERSTOOD EACH OTHER.

115
00:05:09,875 --> 00:05:13,333
I WAS ABLE
TO LEARN EARTHBENDING,
NOT JUST AS A MARTIAL ART

116
00:05:13,375 --> 00:05:17,291
BUT AS AN EXTENSION
OF MY SENSES.

117
00:05:17,333 --> 00:05:20,041
FOR THEM,
THE ORIGINAL EARTHBENDERS,
IT WASN'T JUST ABOUT FIGHTING.

118
00:05:22,250 --> 00:05:26,125
IT WAS THEIR WAY
OF INTERACTING WITH THE WORLD.

119
00:05:26,166 --> 00:05:28,834
Aang: THAT'S AMAZING, TOPH.

120
00:05:28,875 --> 00:05:32,083
I LEARNED FROM THE MONKS,
BUT THE ORIGINAL AIRBENDERS
WERE THE SKY BISON.

121
00:05:32,125 --> 00:05:34,834
MAYBE YOU CAN GIVE ME
A LESSON SOMETIME, BUDDY.

122
00:05:34,875 --> 00:05:36,125
[GROWLING]

123
00:05:36,166 --> 00:05:38,417
WELL, THIS DOESN'T HELP ME.

124
00:05:38,458 --> 00:05:41,542
THE ORIGINAL FIREBENDERS
WERE THE DRAGONS,
AND THEY'RE EXTINCT.

125
00:05:41,583 --> 00:05:43,333
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

126
00:05:43,375 --> 00:05:45,709
ROKU HAD A DRAGON,
AND THERE WERE PLENTY OF DRAGONS
WHEN I WAS A KID.

127
00:05:45,750 --> 00:05:48,583
WELL, THEY AREN'T
AROUND ANYMORE, OK?

128
00:05:48,625 --> 00:05:49,625
OK, OK.

129
00:05:49,667 --> 00:05:51,500
SORRY.

130
00:05:51,542 --> 00:05:54,125
Zuko: BUT MAYBE
THERE'S ANOTHER WAY.

131
00:05:54,166 --> 00:05:56,208
THE FIRST PEOPLE
TO LEARN FROM THE DRAGONS
WERE THE ANCIENT SUN WARRIORS.

132
00:05:57,291 --> 00:05:59,834
Aang: SUN WARRIORS?

133
00:05:59,875 --> 00:06:02,917
WELL, I KNOW<i> THEY</i> WEREN'T AROUND
WHEN I WAS A KID.

134
00:06:02,959 --> 00:06:05,875
NO, THEY DIED OFF
THOUSANDS OF YEARS AGO

135
00:06:05,917 --> 00:06:09,458
BUT THEIR CIVILIZATION WASN'T
TOO FAR FROM WHERE WE ARE NOW.

136
00:06:09,500 --> 00:06:12,333
MAYBE WE CAN LEARN SOMETHING
BY POKING AROUND THE RUINS.

137
00:06:12,375 --> 00:06:14,625
IT'S LIKE THE MONKS
USED TO TELL ME.

138
00:06:14,667 --> 00:06:17,792
SOMETIMES, THE SHADOWS
OF THE PAST CAN BE FELT
BY THE PRESENT.

139
00:06:17,834 --> 00:06:19,625
Sokka: SO WHAT?

140
00:06:19,667 --> 00:06:22,291
MAYBE YOU'LL PICK UP SOME
SUPER OLD SUN WARRIOR ENERGY

141
00:06:22,333 --> 00:06:24,709
JUST BY STANDING WHERE
THEY STOOD 1,000 YEARS AGO?

142
00:06:24,750 --> 00:06:27,208
Zuko: MORE OR LESS.

143
00:06:27,250 --> 00:06:30,166
EITHER I FIND A NEW WAY
TO FIREBEND, OR THE AVATAR
HAS TO FIND A NEW TEACHER.

144
00:06:34,792 --> 00:06:38,917
[WHOOSHING]

145
00:06:38,959 --> 00:06:40,792
WE'VE BEEN RIDING FOR HOURS.

146
00:06:40,834 --> 00:06:43,583
I DON'T KNOW WHY,
BUT I THOUGHT THIS THING
WOULD BE A LOT FASTER.

147
00:06:43,625 --> 00:06:44,792
[GROWLING]

148
00:06:44,834 --> 00:06:47,000
APPA'S RIGHT, ZUKO.

149
00:06:47,041 --> 00:06:50,166
IN OUR GROUP, TYPICALLY,
WE START OUT OUR MISSIONS
WITH A MORE UPBEAT ATTITUDE.

150
00:06:50,208 --> 00:06:51,875
[GROANING]
I CAN'T BELIEVE THIS.

151
00:06:51,917 --> 00:06:53,000
DON'T WORRY.

152
00:06:53,041 --> 00:06:54,750
YOU'LL GET THE HANG OF IT.

153
00:07:02,041 --> 00:07:03,041
WHOA!

154
00:07:07,959 --> 00:07:09,583
Zuko: EVEN THOUGH
THESE BUILDINGS ARE ANCIENT

155
00:07:09,625 --> 00:07:12,709
THERE'S SOMETHING EERILY
FAMILIAR ABOUT THEM.

156
00:07:12,750 --> 00:07:15,500
I CAN TELL THE FIRE SAGES'
TEMPLES ARE SOMEHOW
DESCENDED FROM THESE.

157
00:07:15,542 --> 00:07:18,458
OK, WE'VE LEARNED SOMETHING
ABOUT ARCHITECTURE.

158
00:07:18,500 --> 00:07:21,083
HOPEFULLY, WE'LL LEARN SOMETHING
ABOUT FIREBENDING TOO.

159
00:07:21,125 --> 00:07:22,583
THE PAST CAN BE A GREAT TEACHER.

160
00:07:22,625 --> 00:07:26,417
[SCREAMING]

161
00:07:26,458 --> 00:07:27,458
[AANG GRUNTING]

162
00:07:27,500 --> 00:07:29,250
[WHIMPERING]

163
00:07:29,291 --> 00:07:32,917
ZUKO, I THINK THE PAST
IS TRYING TO KILL ME.

164
00:07:32,959 --> 00:07:34,542
I CAN'T BELIEVE IT.

165
00:07:34,583 --> 00:07:37,709
THIS BOOBY TRAP MUST
BE CENTURIES OLD,
AND IT STILL WORKS.

166
00:07:37,750 --> 00:07:39,208
THERE'S PROBABLY A LOT MORE.

167
00:07:39,250 --> 00:07:40,500
MAYBE THIS MEANS
WE SHOULDN'T BE HERE.

168
00:07:44,959 --> 00:07:48,709
WHERE'S THAT UPBEAT ATTITUDE
YOU WERE TALKING ABOUT?

169
00:07:48,750 --> 00:07:52,417
BESIDES, PEOPLE DON'T MAKE TRAPS
UNLESS THEY'VE GOT
SOMETHING WORTH PROTECTING.

170
00:07:55,959 --> 00:07:56,917
LOOK.

171
00:07:56,959 --> 00:07:58,875
THIS SEEMS PROMISING.

172
00:07:58,917 --> 00:08:02,375
THOUGH I'M NOT SURE WHAT
THIS TELLS US ABOUT THE ORIGINAL
SOURCE OF FIREBENDING.

173
00:08:02,417 --> 00:08:05,166
THEY LOOK PRETTY ANGRY TO ME.

174
00:08:05,208 --> 00:08:07,917
Aang: I THOUGHT THE DRAGONS WERE
FRIENDS WITH THE SUN WARRIORS.

175
00:08:07,959 --> 00:08:10,250
Zuko: WELL, THEY HAD
A FUNNY WAY OF SHOWING IT.

176
00:08:14,291 --> 00:08:17,041
ZUKO, SOMETHING HAPPENED
TO THE DRAGONS IN
THE LAST 100 YEARS.

177
00:08:17,083 --> 00:08:20,041
SOMETHING YOU'RE NOT TELLING ME.

178
00:08:20,083 --> 00:08:22,709
MY GREAT-GRANDFATHER
SOZIN HAPPENED.

179
00:08:22,750 --> 00:08:26,041
HE STARTED THE TRADITION
OF HUNTING DRAGONS FOR GLORY.

180
00:08:26,083 --> 00:08:28,333
THEY WERE
THE ULTIMATE FIREBENDERS

181
00:08:28,375 --> 00:08:31,834
AND IF YOU COULD CONQUER ONE,
YOUR FIREBENDING TALENTS
WOULD BECOME LEGENDARY

182
00:08:31,875 --> 00:08:34,208
AND YOU'D EARN
THE HONORARY TITLE, DRAGON.

183
00:08:34,250 --> 00:08:39,208
THE LAST GREAT DRAGON
WAS CONQUERED LONG BEFORE
I WAS BORN, BY MY UNCLE.

184
00:08:41,250 --> 00:08:45,542
BUT I THOUGHT YOUR UNCLE WAS,
I DON'T KNOW, GOOD?

185
00:08:45,583 --> 00:08:47,834
HE HAD A COMPLICATED PAST.

186
00:08:47,875 --> 00:08:49,917
FAMILY TRADITION, I GUESS.

187
00:08:51,917 --> 00:08:53,166
LET'S JUST MOVE ON.

188
00:09:00,166 --> 00:09:04,083
[GRUNTING]

189
00:09:04,125 --> 00:09:05,417
IT'S LOCKED UP.

190
00:09:08,542 --> 00:09:09,667
WAIT.

191
00:09:09,709 --> 00:09:12,667
IT'S A CELESTIAL CALENDAR.

192
00:09:12,709 --> 00:09:16,458
JUST LIKE THE FIRE SAGES
HAVE IN THEIR TEMPLES.

193
00:09:16,500 --> 00:09:18,917
I BET THAT SUN STONE
OPENS THE DOOR

194
00:09:18,959 --> 00:09:21,291
BUT ONLY WHEN SUNLIGHT HITS IT
AT JUST THE RIGHT ANGLE,
ON THE SOLSTICE.

195
00:09:22,417 --> 00:09:23,583
MONKEY FEATHERS.

196
00:09:23,625 --> 00:09:25,000
THE SOLSTICE AGAIN.

197
00:09:25,041 --> 00:09:26,500
WE CAN'T WAIT HERE THAT LONG.

198
00:09:26,542 --> 00:09:28,417
NO, WE CAN'T.

199
00:09:28,458 --> 00:09:31,166
BUT WE MIGHT BE ABLE
TO SPEED TIME UP.

200
00:09:31,208 --> 00:09:33,166
LET'S SEE IF WE CAN OUTSMART
THE SUN STONE.

201
00:09:37,625 --> 00:09:38,875
NOTHING'S HAPPENING.

202
00:09:38,917 --> 00:09:40,333
COME ON.

203
00:09:40,375 --> 00:09:43,500
[RUMBLING]

204
00:09:43,542 --> 00:09:48,583
YOU KNOW, ZUKO, I DON'T CARE
WHAT EVERYONE ELSE
SAYS ABOUT YOU.

205
00:09:48,625 --> 00:09:49,458
YOU'RE PRETTY SMART.

206
00:09:56,125 --> 00:09:57,083
[GASPING]

207
00:09:57,125 --> 00:09:58,500
RELAX.

208
00:09:58,542 --> 00:09:59,750
THEY'RE JUST STATUES.

209
00:10:05,875 --> 00:10:10,000
IT SAYS THIS IS SOMETHING
CALLED THE DANCING DRAGON.

210
00:10:21,709 --> 00:10:23,458
ZUKO, GET OVER HERE.

211
00:10:23,500 --> 00:10:24,917
I WANT YOU TO DANCE WITH ME.

212
00:10:24,959 --> 00:10:25,959
WHAT?

213
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:27,709
JUST DO IT.

214
00:10:27,750 --> 00:10:29,375
[ZUKO GROANING]

215
00:10:29,417 --> 00:10:30,625
LET'S FOLLOW THE STEPS
OF THE STATUES.

216
00:10:35,667 --> 00:10:36,709
DON'T YOU SEE?

217
00:10:36,750 --> 00:10:38,500
THESE AREN'T DANCE MOVES.

218
00:10:38,542 --> 00:10:40,542
THESE STATUES ARE GIVING US
A LESSON.

219
00:10:40,583 --> 00:10:44,667
I THINK THIS IS SOME KIND
OF SUN WARRIOR FIREBENDING FORM.

220
00:10:44,709 --> 00:10:46,500
THIS BETTER TEACH US
SOME REALLY GOOD FIREBENDING.

221
00:10:54,917 --> 00:10:56,500
HOORAY!

222
00:10:56,542 --> 00:10:57,834
WAIT.

223
00:10:57,875 --> 00:11:00,166
WHAT EXACTLY IS THAT?

224
00:11:00,208 --> 00:11:02,000
IT'S SOME KIND
OF MYSTICAL GEMSTONE.

225
00:11:02,041 --> 00:11:03,166
WELL, DON'T TOUCH IT.

226
00:11:03,208 --> 00:11:05,208
WHY NOT?

227
00:11:05,250 --> 00:11:07,375
REMEMBER WHAT HAPPENED OUT THERE
WITH THOSE SPIKES?

228
00:11:07,417 --> 00:11:10,500
I'M JUST VERY SUSPICIOUS
OF GIANT, GLOWING GEMS
SITTING ON PEDESTALS.

229
00:11:12,917 --> 00:11:16,166
IT FEELS ALMOST ALIVE.

230
00:11:16,208 --> 00:11:18,625
[SCREAMING]

231
00:11:18,667 --> 00:11:20,875
OH, NO, IT'S ANOTHER TRAP.

232
00:11:23,583 --> 00:11:24,709
[GROANING]

233
00:11:24,750 --> 00:11:26,083
I CAN'T PULL FREE.

234
00:11:26,125 --> 00:11:27,208
IT'S LIKE SOME KIND OF GLUE.

235
00:11:33,458 --> 00:11:35,667
[GRUNTING]

236
00:11:35,709 --> 00:11:36,583
[GRUNTING]

237
00:11:40,500 --> 00:11:42,166
[GROANING]

238
00:11:44,625 --> 00:11:47,834
I CAN'T MOVE.

239
00:11:47,875 --> 00:11:49,208
ZUKO, DO SOMETHING.

240
00:11:49,250 --> 00:11:50,375
ME?

241
00:11:50,417 --> 00:11:51,792
I CAN'T MOVE EITHER.

242
00:11:54,667 --> 00:11:57,375
[GROANING]

243
00:11:57,417 --> 00:11:59,417
IT STOPPED.

244
00:11:59,458 --> 00:12:01,375
AT LEAST WE HAVE AIR.

245
00:12:01,417 --> 00:12:03,375
MAYBE IF WE STAY CALM,
WE CAN FIGURE A WAY OUT OF THIS.

246
00:12:10,125 --> 00:12:14,750
YOU HAD TO PICK UP
THE GLOWING EGG, DIDN'T YOU?

247
00:12:14,792 --> 00:12:16,917
AT LEAST I MADE
SOMETHING HAPPEN.

248
00:12:16,959 --> 00:12:19,291
IF IT WERE UP TO YOU, WE'D NEVER
HAVE MADE IT PAST THE COURTYARD.

249
00:12:19,333 --> 00:12:21,000
HELP!

250
00:12:21,041 --> 00:12:23,208
WHO ARE YOU YELLING TO?

251
00:12:23,250 --> 00:12:25,417
NOBODY'S LIVED HERE
FOR CENTURIES.

252
00:12:25,458 --> 00:12:28,542
WELL, WHAT DO<i> YOU</i> THINK
WE SHOULD DO?

253
00:12:28,583 --> 00:12:30,792
THINK ABOUT OUR PLACE
IN THE UNIVERSE?

254
00:12:30,834 --> 00:12:33,542
[SIGHING]

255
00:12:36,500 --> 00:12:37,750
WHO IS DOWN THERE?

256
00:12:51,542 --> 00:12:55,667
FOR TRYING TO TAKE
OUR SUN STONE, YOU MUST
BE SEVERELY PUNISHED.

257
00:12:55,709 --> 00:12:58,125
WE DIDN'T COME HERE
TO TAKE YOUR SUN STONE.

258
00:12:58,166 --> 00:13:01,500
WE CAME HERE TO FIND
THE ANCIENT ORIGIN
OF ALL FIREBENDING.

259
00:13:01,542 --> 00:13:03,208
Man: YEAH, RIGHT.

260
00:13:03,250 --> 00:13:06,291
THEY ARE OBVIOUSLY THIEVES,
HERE TO STEAL
SUN WARRIOR TREASURES.

261
00:13:06,333 --> 00:13:08,250
Aang: PLEASE.

262
00:13:08,291 --> 00:13:11,875
I DON'T NORMALLY PLAY THIS CARD,
BUT I'M THE AVATAR.

263
00:13:17,041 --> 00:13:18,250
JUST HEAR US OUT.

264
00:13:18,291 --> 00:13:22,208
MY NAME IS ZUKO,
CROWN PRINCE OF THE FIRE NATION.

265
00:13:22,250 --> 00:13:25,000
OR AT LEAST, I USED TO BE.

266
00:13:25,041 --> 00:13:29,125
I KNOW MY PEOPLE HAVE DISTORTED
THE WAYS OF FIREBENDING,
TO BE FUELLED BY ANGER AND RAGE

267
00:13:29,166 --> 00:13:33,875
BUT NOW I WANT TO LEARN
THE TRUE WAY, THE ORIGINAL WAY.

268
00:13:33,917 --> 00:13:38,500
WHEN WE CAME HERE, I NEVER
IMAGINED THE SUN WARRIOR
CIVILIZATION WAS SECRETLY ALIVE.

269
00:13:38,542 --> 00:13:41,542
I AM TRULY HUMBLED
TO BE IN YOUR PRESENCE.

270
00:13:41,583 --> 00:13:43,458
PLEASE, TEACH US.

271
00:13:43,500 --> 00:13:47,166
IF YOU WISH TO LEARN
THE WAYS OF THE SUN

272
00:13:47,208 --> 00:13:50,583
YOU MUST LEARN THEM FROM
THE MASTERS RAN AND SHAO.

273
00:13:50,834 --> 00:13:52,583
RAN AND SHAO?

274
00:13:52,625 --> 00:13:54,834
THERE ARE TWO OF THEM?

275
00:13:54,875 --> 00:13:58,834
WHEN YOU PRESENT YOURSELVES
TO THEM, THEY WILL EXAMINE YOU.

276
00:13:58,875 --> 00:14:03,458
THEY'LL READ YOUR HEARTS,
YOUR SOULS, AND YOUR ANCESTRY.

277
00:14:03,500 --> 00:14:05,834
IF THEY DEEM YOU WORTHY,
THEY'LL TEACH YOU.

278
00:14:05,875 --> 00:14:10,000
IF THEY DON'T, YOU'LL BE
DESTROYED ON THE SPOT.

279
00:14:17,709 --> 00:14:21,667
Chief: IF YOU'RE GOING TO SEE
THE MASTERS, YOU MUST BRING THEM
A PIECE OF THE ETERNAL FLAME.

280
00:14:23,959 --> 00:14:28,458
THIS FIRE IS THE VERY FIRST ONE.

281
00:14:28,500 --> 00:14:31,583
IT WAS GIVEN TO MAN
BY THE DRAGONS.

282
00:14:31,625 --> 00:14:34,500
WE HAVE KEPT IT GOING
FOR THOUSANDS OF YEARS.

283
00:14:34,542 --> 00:14:36,583
I DON'T BELIEVE IT.

284
00:14:36,625 --> 00:14:40,166
Chief: YOU WILL EACH TAKE
A PIECE OF IT TO THE MASTERS

285
00:14:40,208 --> 00:14:43,208
TO SHOW YOUR COMMITMENT TO
THE SACRED ART OF FIREBENDING.

286
00:14:43,250 --> 00:14:47,041
UM, MISTER SUN CHIEF, SIR?

287
00:14:47,083 --> 00:14:50,083
YEAH, I'M NOT A FIREBENDER YET.

288
00:14:50,125 --> 00:14:52,166
COULDN'T MY FRIEND HERE
CARRY MY FIRE FOR ME?

289
00:14:52,208 --> 00:14:53,667
NO.

290
00:14:58,750 --> 00:15:03,959
THIS RITUAL ILLUSTRATES
THE ESSENCE OF
SUN WARRIOR PHILOSOPHY.

291
00:15:04,000 --> 00:15:06,875
YOU MUST MAINTAIN
A CONSTANT HEAT.

292
00:15:06,917 --> 00:15:10,125
THE FLAME WILL GO OUT
IF YOU MAKE IT TOO SMALL.

293
00:15:10,166 --> 00:15:13,000
MAKE IT TOO BIG,
AND YOU MIGHT LOSE CONTROL.

294
00:15:16,458 --> 00:15:17,667
I'M SORRY.

295
00:15:17,709 --> 00:15:20,375
I'M JUST A LITTLE NERVOUS.

296
00:15:20,417 --> 00:15:24,709
IT'S LIKE A LITTLE HEARTBEAT.

297
00:15:24,750 --> 00:15:28,709
FIRE IS LIFE,
NOT JUST DESTRUCTION.

298
00:15:28,750 --> 00:15:30,583
YOU WILL TAKE
YOUR FLAMES UP THERE.

299
00:15:30,625 --> 00:15:34,333
THE CAVE OF THE MASTERS
IS BENEATH THAT ROCK.

300
00:15:44,125 --> 00:15:45,709
HURRY UP.

301
00:15:45,750 --> 00:15:47,542
I CAN'T.

302
00:15:47,583 --> 00:15:49,333
IF I WALK TOO FAST,
MY FLAME'LL GO OUT.

303
00:15:49,375 --> 00:15:51,166
YOUR FLAME'S GONNA GO OUT
BECAUSE IT'S TOO SMALL.

304
00:15:51,208 --> 00:15:52,542
YOU'RE TOO TIMID.

305
00:15:52,583 --> 00:15:53,875
GIVE IT MORE JUICE.

306
00:15:53,917 --> 00:15:55,625
BUT WHAT IF I CAN'T CONTROL IT?

307
00:15:55,667 --> 00:15:56,750
YOU CAN DO IT.

308
00:15:56,792 --> 00:15:58,083
I KNOW YOU CAN.

309
00:15:58,125 --> 00:15:58,917
YOU'RE A TALENTED KID.

310
00:16:13,834 --> 00:16:16,750
FACING THE JUDGMENT
OF THE FIREBENDING MASTERS
WILL BE VERY DANGEROUS FOR YOU.

311
00:16:19,834 --> 00:16:25,083
YOUR ANCESTORS
ARE DIRECTLY RESPONSIBLE
FOR THE DRAGONS' DISAPPEARANCE.

312
00:16:25,125 --> 00:16:28,458
THE MASTERS MIGHT NOT BE
SO HAPPY TO SEE YOU.

313
00:16:28,500 --> 00:16:31,208
I KNOW I WOULDN'T BE.

314
00:16:31,250 --> 00:16:32,834
BUT ONCE THEY FIND OUT
I'M THE AVATAR...

315
00:16:32,875 --> 00:16:35,500
HAVE YOU FORGOTTEN
THAT YOU VANISHED

316
00:16:35,542 --> 00:16:38,500
ALLOWING THE FIRE NATION
TO WREAK HAVOC ON THE WORLD?

317
00:16:38,542 --> 00:16:41,083
THE DECLINE OF THE DRAGONS
IS YOUR BURDEN TOO.

318
00:16:53,583 --> 00:16:56,709
WE COULD TURN BACK NOW.

319
00:16:56,750 --> 00:16:59,458
WE'VE ALREADY LEARNED MORE
ABOUT FIRE THAN WE'D HOPED.

320
00:16:59,500 --> 00:17:03,291
NO, WE'RE SEEING THIS
THROUGH TO THE END.

321
00:17:03,333 --> 00:17:05,542
WE'RE GONNA MEET THESE MASTERS
AND FIND OUT WHAT'S
SO GREAT ABOUT THEM.

322
00:17:05,583 --> 00:17:08,834
WHAT IF THEY JUDGE US
AND ATTACK US?

323
00:17:08,875 --> 00:17:10,875
WELL, WE'RE THE FIRE PRINCE
AND THE AVATAR.

324
00:17:10,917 --> 00:17:13,250
I THINK WE COULD TAKE THESE GUYS
IN A FIGHT, WHOEVER THEY ARE.

325
00:17:19,375 --> 00:17:21,333
BRING 'EM OUT.

326
00:17:21,375 --> 00:17:23,417
CHANTERS!

327
00:17:23,458 --> 00:17:28,792
[MEN VOCALIZING RHYTHMICALLY...]

328
00:18:09,041 --> 00:18:13,542
THOSE WHO WISH TO MEET
THE MASTERS RAN AND SHAO
WILL NOW PRESENT THEIR FIRE.

329
00:18:18,959 --> 00:18:22,709
SOUND THE CALL.

330
00:18:22,750 --> 00:18:25,333
[HORN BLOWING]

331
00:18:25,375 --> 00:18:27,083
[CRASHING]

332
00:18:29,458 --> 00:18:30,875
WHAT'S HAPPENING?

333
00:18:35,166 --> 00:18:36,333
[GASPING]

334
00:18:36,375 --> 00:18:37,458
ZUKO, MY FIRE WENT OUT.

335
00:18:37,500 --> 00:18:39,041
WHAT DO YOU WANT ME TO DO?

336
00:18:39,083 --> 00:18:40,291
GIVE ME SOME OF YOURS.

337
00:18:40,333 --> 00:18:41,417
[GRUNTING]

338
00:18:41,458 --> 00:18:42,333
NO, JUST MAKE YOUR OWN.

339
00:18:42,375 --> 00:18:43,250
I CAN'T.

340
00:18:43,291 --> 00:18:44,417
[GRUNTING]

341
00:18:44,458 --> 00:18:45,792
Zuko: GET SOME FROM ONE
OF THOSE WARRIORS.

342
00:18:45,834 --> 00:18:47,041
HURRY.

343
00:18:47,083 --> 00:18:48,250
STOP CHEATING OFF ME.

344
00:18:48,291 --> 00:18:49,542
Aang: QUIT BEING STINGY.

345
00:18:49,583 --> 00:18:54,083
[BOTH GRUNTING]

346
00:18:56,834 --> 00:18:58,250
[CRASHING]

347
00:18:58,291 --> 00:19:00,166
Both: UH-OH.

348
00:19:02,625 --> 00:19:03,500
[DRAGON GROWLING]

349
00:19:16,083 --> 00:19:17,959
THESE ARE THE MASTERS.

350
00:19:18,000 --> 00:19:19,583
YOU STILL THINK WE CAN TAKE 'EM?

351
00:19:19,625 --> 00:19:20,750
SHH.

352
00:19:20,792 --> 00:19:22,083
I NEVER SAID THAT.

353
00:19:25,792 --> 00:19:30,166
OH, HERE IT COMES.

354
00:19:30,208 --> 00:19:31,458
ANY MOMENT NOW.

355
00:19:31,500 --> 00:19:33,291
DINNER FOR THE MASTERS.

356
00:19:33,333 --> 00:19:34,375
QUIET, HAM GHAO.

357
00:19:34,417 --> 00:19:35,917
WHAT?

358
00:19:35,959 --> 00:19:36,917
EVERYONE'S THINKING IT.

359
00:19:45,667 --> 00:19:48,917
ZUKO, I THINK WE'RE SUPPOSED TO
DO THE DRAGON DANCE WITH THEM.

360
00:19:48,959 --> 00:19:51,125
WHAT?

361
00:19:51,166 --> 00:19:53,792
WHAT ABOUT THIS SITUATION
MAKES YOU THINK
THEY WANT US TO DANCE?

362
00:19:53,834 --> 00:19:56,709
WELL, I THINK THEY
WANT US TO DO SOMETHING.

363
00:19:56,750 --> 00:19:58,417
LET'S JUST TRY IT.

364
00:19:58,458 --> 00:19:59,125
FINE.

365
00:20:25,917 --> 00:20:27,625
JUDGMENT TIME.

366
00:20:27,667 --> 00:20:30,291
[DRAGON GROWLING]

367
00:20:32,083 --> 00:20:32,917
[WHIMPERING]

368
00:20:36,875 --> 00:20:38,792
[AANG AND ZUKO SCREAMING]

369
00:20:49,250 --> 00:20:51,667
[GASPING]

370
00:20:51,709 --> 00:20:53,500
I UNDERSTAND.

371
00:21:15,583 --> 00:21:17,500
THEIR FIRE WAS BEAUTIFUL.

372
00:21:17,542 --> 00:21:21,208
I SAW SO MANY COLORS,
COLORS I'VE NEVER IMAGINED.

373
00:21:21,250 --> 00:21:23,291
Aang: LIKE FIREBENDING HARMONY.

374
00:21:23,333 --> 00:21:26,041
YES.

375
00:21:26,083 --> 00:21:30,875
THEY JUDGED YOU,
AND GAVE YOU VISIONS OF
THE MEANING OF FIREBENDING.

376
00:21:30,917 --> 00:21:33,083
I CAN'T BELIEVE THERE
ARE STILL LIVING DRAGONS.

377
00:21:33,125 --> 00:21:36,250
MY UNCLE IROH SAID HE FACED
THE LAST DRAGON AND KILLED IT.

378
00:21:36,291 --> 00:21:38,041
SO YOUR UNCLE LIED.

379
00:21:38,083 --> 00:21:41,959
ACTUALLY, IT WASN'T A TOTAL LIE.

380
00:21:42,000 --> 00:21:45,667
IROH WAS THE LAST OUTSIDER
TO FACE THE MASTERS.

381
00:21:45,709 --> 00:21:51,417
THEY DEEMED HIM WORTHY
AND PASSED THE SECRET
ON TO HIM AS WELL.

382
00:21:51,458 --> 00:21:54,959
Zuko: HE MUST'VE LIED
TO PROTECT THEM, SO NO ONE
ELSE WOULD HUNT THEM.

383
00:21:55,000 --> 00:21:59,875
ALL THIS TIME, I THOUGHT
FIREBENDING WAS DESTRUCTION.

384
00:21:59,917 --> 00:22:03,500
SINCE I HURT KATARA, I'VE BEEN
TOO AFRAID AND HESITANT

385
00:22:03,542 --> 00:22:05,750
BUT NOW I KNOW
WHAT IT REALLY IS.

386
00:22:05,792 --> 00:22:08,333
IT'S ENERGY, AND LIFE.

387
00:22:08,375 --> 00:22:10,083
YEAH.

388
00:22:10,125 --> 00:22:12,166
IT'S LIKE THE SUN,
BUT INSIDE OF YOU.

389
00:22:12,208 --> 00:22:14,208
DO YOU GUYS REALIZE THIS?

390
00:22:14,250 --> 00:22:18,250
WELL, OUR CIVILIZATION IS CALLED
THE SUN WARRIORS, SO YEAH.

391
00:22:20,250 --> 00:22:22,959
THAT'S WHY MY FIREBENDING
WAS SO WEAK BEFORE

392
00:22:23,000 --> 00:22:26,250
BECAUSE FOR SO MANY YEARS,
HUNTING YOU WAS MY DRIVE.

393
00:22:26,291 --> 00:22:28,125
IT WAS MY PURPOSE.

394
00:22:28,166 --> 00:22:31,959
SO WHEN I JOINED YOU,
I LOST SIGHT OF MY INNER FIRE.

395
00:22:32,000 --> 00:22:35,750
BUT NOW, I HAVE A NEW DRIVE.

396
00:22:35,792 --> 00:22:38,750
I HAVE TO HELP YOU
DEFEAT MY FATHER AND RESTORE
BALANCE TO THE WORLD.

397
00:22:49,959 --> 00:22:54,875
NOW THAT YOU HAVE LEARNED
THE SECRETS AND YOU KNOW
ABOUT OUR TRIBE'S EXISTENCE

398
00:22:57,125 --> 00:23:01,458
WE HAVE NO CHOICE BUT
TO IMPRISON YOU HERE FOREVER.

399
00:23:03,792 --> 00:23:06,333
JUST KIDDING.

400
00:23:06,375 --> 00:23:11,000
BUT SERIOUSLY,
DON'T TELL ANYONE.

401
00:23:11,041 --> 00:23:14,458
Aang: WITH THIS TECHNIQUE
THE DRAGONS SHOWED US,
ZUKO AND I WILL BE UNSTOPPABLE.

402
00:23:19,041 --> 00:23:21,166
[APPLAUSE]

403
00:23:21,208 --> 00:23:23,000
Sokka: YEAH, THAT'S A GREAT
DANCE YOU TWO LEARNED THERE.

404
00:23:23,041 --> 00:23:24,208
IT'S NOT A DANCE.

405
00:23:24,250 --> 00:23:26,333
IT'S A FIREBENDING FORM.

406
00:23:26,375 --> 00:23:29,125
WE'LL JUST TAP DANCE OUR WAY
TO VICTORY OVER THE FIRE LORD.

407
00:23:29,166 --> 00:23:32,875
IT'S A SACRED FORM THAT HAPPENS
TO BE THOUSANDS OF YEARS OLD.

408
00:23:32,917 --> 00:23:34,000
OH, YEAH?

409
00:23:34,041 --> 00:23:37,291
WHAT'S YOUR LITTLE FORM CALLED?

410
00:23:37,333 --> 00:23:39,000
THE DANCING DRAGON.

411
00:23:39,041 --> 00:23:42,333
[LAUGHTER]

412
00:23:50,208 --> 00:23:52,917
[MEN VOCALIZING RHYTHMICALLY...]

413
00:23:52,959 --> 00:23:55,959
♪
